DBEM - Leginon Database Tools


-------------
Requirements:
-------------
- Web server Apache
- MySQL (4.0 or higher)
- PHP4 (4.0.4 or higher) with MySQL 
- JavaScript-enabled browser
- CSS-enabled browser


----------
Unpacking:
----------

Unpack the archive into your web server directory:
	$ cd /yourwwwdir
	$ tar zxvf dbem.tgz
	$ cd scheduler                                 

--------------
Configuration:
--------------
	$ cd dbem

	- edit the file config.php
	- set your MySQL parameters:

	$HOSTNAME = "[SQL HOST]";
	$DBUSER = "[SQL USER]";
	$DBPASSWORD = "[SQL PASS]";
	$DATABASE = "[database]";

--------------
run:
--------------
	Go to http://yourhost/dbem/

